226
00:17:16,099 --> 00:17:18,155
Eu nunca vou sair desta cama.

227
00:17:19,629 --> 00:17:22,555
Mesa, que tal nossa viagem para Tha Chang?

228
00:17:25,975 --> 00:17:27,975
Maldito!

229
00:17:35,981 --> 00:17:37,808
