247
00:18:59,718 --> 00:19:00,686
OK.

248
00:19:01,126 --> 00:19:01,834
Claro.

249
00:19:03,795 --> 00:19:04,849
O que é?

250
00:19:06,852 --> 00:19:09,242
Minha mãe…

251
00:19:09,963 --> 00:19:11,367
está convidando você para vir.

252
00:19:12,103 --> 00:19:12,872
Realmente?

253
00:19:13,531 --> 00:19:14,305
Mas

254
00:19:15,531 --> 00:19:18,273
se você não quiser, tudo bem.

255
00:19:18,771 --> 00:19:19,691
Entendo.

256
00:19:21,510 --> 00:19:22,590
